WEBVTT

00:01.565 --> 00:03.307
-ANNOUNCER: LAST TIME,
ON BAYWATCH.

00:03.438 --> 00:05.483
-JESSE, THIS IS JAKE BARNES.
USUALLY WORKS UP AT ZUMA BEACH.

00:07.703 --> 00:09.096
-JAKE.

00:09.226 --> 00:10.532
-ERIC, WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

00:10.662 --> 00:11.881
-WE NEED TO TALK.

00:15.363 --> 00:16.451
CLARE'S DEAD.

00:20.411 --> 00:22.892
THERE'S SOMETHING
ELSE, THE CHILD.

00:24.546 --> 00:28.202
HE'S YOUR SON, AND
HIS NAME'S TERRENCE.

00:28.767 --> 00:30.160
-PEOPLE ARE IN TROUBLE,
WE RUN TO HELP THEM.

00:30.291 --> 00:32.162
-YEAH, IN THE WATER.

00:32.293 --> 00:34.251
SOMEONE I DON'T KNOW,
A STRANGER,
I'M GOOD WITH STRANGERS.

00:35.078 --> 00:36.906
'CAUSE I CAN PULL THEM
OUT, AND I CAN WALK AWAY.

00:37.037 --> 00:38.299
-DON'T WALK AWAY FROM THIS ONE.

00:41.258 --> 00:42.216
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

00:44.087 --> 00:45.480
I'LL GO WITH YOU.

00:45.610 --> 00:47.308
WHAT KIND OF RACE
ARE WE TALKING ABOUT?

00:47.438 --> 00:50.354
-IT'S A HYBRID.
PART ECO STYLE, PART IRON MAN,

00:50.485 --> 00:51.877
A LITTLE TRIATHLON.

00:52.008 --> 00:53.749
-WOMAN: SOUNDS LIKE
WE SHOULD GO TO AUSTRALIA.

00:53.879 --> 00:57.144
-MITCH: IT'S A CITY OF WONDER
IN A LAND DOWN UNDER.

00:57.274 --> 00:59.189
-ERIC TOLD ME TO EXPECT YOU.

00:59.320 --> 01:00.669
I'M ALLIE REESE.

01:02.236 --> 01:03.933
I WAS CLARE'S BEST FRIEND.

01:06.240 --> 01:08.546
-WOMAN: HELP!
SOMEBODY HELP!

01:09.460 --> 01:12.594
HE'S DROWNING! HURRY, HELP!

01:13.160 --> 01:14.726
SOMEBODY!

01:15.858 --> 01:20.167
[RACING MUSIC]

01:21.559 --> 01:22.647
-WHAT'S TERRY DOING HERE?

01:23.431 --> 01:24.867
-CLARE WAS A MEMBER,

01:24.997 --> 01:26.956
BUT HE CAN'T CONTINUE
TO STAY, NOT ALONE.

01:27.870 --> 01:28.740
-WHERE IS HE NOW?

01:29.393 --> 01:31.569
-ALLIE: HE'S PROBABLY
AT THE ROCK WALL.

01:34.529 --> 01:35.399
-ARE YOU MY DAD?

01:37.923 --> 01:41.275
-YES, TERRY, I'M YOUR DAD.

01:43.103 --> 01:44.408
-ARE YOU GOING TO STAY WITH ME?

01:44.539 --> 01:48.934
-YES, FOREVER, AND
THAT'S A PROMISE, OKAY?

01:50.153 --> 01:52.634
-WELL, IF YOU'RE GONNA STAY,
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO Q.

01:52.764 --> 01:54.549
-Q?

01:54.679 --> 01:56.768
-AS IN QUALIFY, PASS A
PHYSICAL TEST FOR MEMBERSHIP.

01:56.899 --> 01:59.510
-NO, NO, NO, THANK YOU, BUT
AS SOON AS I GET TERRY PACKED,

01:59.641 --> 02:02.078
HE AND I ARE GOING HOME,
BACK TO CALIFORNIA.

02:05.342 --> 02:10.347
♪ [THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

02:13.307 --> 02:16.136
♪ SOME PEOPLE STAND
IN THE DARKNESS ♪

02:17.137 --> 02:20.705
♪ AFRAID TO STEP
INTO THE LIGHT ♪

02:20.836 --> 02:24.840
♪ SOME PEOPLE NEED
