02:25.449 --> 02:28.496
♪ WHEN THE EDGE OF
SURRENDER'S IN SIGHT ♪

02:28.626 --> 02:30.802
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY

02:31.847 --> 02:34.241
♪ IT'S GONNA BE ALRIGHT

02:37.331 --> 02:39.115
♪ 'CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY

02:39.246 --> 02:43.424
♪ I WON'T LET YOU
